com.gsma.mobileconnect.oidc

Class RequestTokenResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gsma.mobileconnect.oidc.RequestTokenResponse

  • public class RequestTokenResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to hold the response of IOIDC.requestToken(DiscoveryResponse, String, String, TokenOptions, IRequestTokenCallback)

    Will contain either an error response or request data.
